Step 6: Restart the EBS CSI controller

Back on your EC2 instance:

kubectl rollout restart deployment ebs-csi-controller -n kube-system

Wait 1–2 minutes and check:

kubectl get pods -n kube-system

The EBS CSI controller pods should move from:

CrashLoopBackOff

to:

6/6 Running

