12. Common Interview Question

Deployment vs StatefulSet

| Feature          | Deployment | StatefulSet |
| ---------------- | ---------- | ----------- |
| Stable Pod Name  | ❌          | ✅           |
| Stable Storage   | ❌          | ✅           |
| Ordered Startup  | ❌          | ✅           |
| Ordered Shutdown | ❌          | ✅           |
| Headless Service | ❌          | ✅           |
| Databases        | ❌          | ✅           |
| Stateless Apps   | ✅          | ❌           |




